       Name: Arcane Lock
       Kind: Spell
     Target: TAR_IGNORE
   Position: POS_STANDING
   Min Mana: 15
 Wait Beats: 24
 Can Learn: FALSE
Noun Damage:
   Wear-Off: !Arcane Lock!
Acquisition:
